modName: A Melody By Whale _ Main Menu Music Replacer
summary: This is a simple, and peaceful sang by me, you're favorite whale friend. I hope you all enjoy this mod as much as I do.
descriptionHtml: This mod replaces the main menu's music into a melody sang/hummed by me. This melody may not sound good to most people, although it may just be the most beautiful thing you've ever heard.
author: Me
